    "Methane Emissions.",
    "Human activities emitting methane include leaks from natural gas systems and the raising of livestock.",
    "Methane is also emitted by natural sources such as termites.",
    "In addition, natural processes in soil and chemical reactions in the atmosphere help remove CH4 from the atmosphere.",
